node.title: Cyclist dies after colliding with truck on SH6, Wakefield
node.description: A cyclist has died after colliding with a truck in Wakefield, Tasman District this afternoon.
node.content:
["A cyclist has died after colliding with a truck in Wakefield, Tasman District this afternoon.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Claire Eastham-Farrelly\n
", "Police said the accident happened on SH6 between Baigent Valley Road and Hoult Valley Road West shortly before 5pm.", "The highway remains closed while emergency services are at the scene."]
